{"tid":110711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[證據確鑿] ICAC 唔該拉鳩中央/明報/01","createTime":"2017-02-07T01:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T15:04:51.000Z","uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc54ae591ad72564f79a7a8761a76a6f61765613","tid":110711,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例<br />\n<br />\n26 發布關於候選人的虛假或具誤導性的陳述的非法行為<br />\n<br />\n(1) 任何人為促使或阻礙某候選人或某些候選人當選，而發布關於該候選人或該等候選人且屬虛假<br />\n達關鍵程度或具誤導性達關鍵程度的事實陳述，即屬在選舉中作出非法行為。"},{"pid":"f5d26d47b791f24594a01343e5a6f2102f3729af","tid":110711,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"send 信去icac會唔會有幫助?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1125e8f472ac4b049506a3db0c496c9a3c5ab28","tid":110711,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"越睇越似係假消息"}]}